ten in bold yellow letters against a black background, with the hashtag '[text2]' in smaller red text underneath. A metallic house key is attached to the keychain ring. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible. High-quality macro photography, soft natural lighting, shallow depth of field, sharp focus on the keychain textures.","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Name on keychain\",\"value\":\"NAEEM MEHMOOD\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Hashtag description\",\"value\":\"#AI Graphic Designer\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1774506866823.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1774506866823.png","thumbSize":"374,512","type":"image"},{"time":1774506046227,"name":"instagram profile","tags":"social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"Photorealistic high-end commercial studio portrait. A subject wearing light beige traditional attire (kurta) is seated in a plush gray velvet armchair with gold legs in the foreground. The subject is wearing dark brown sandals, posed with legs crossed. In the background, dominating the scene, is a massive, vertically oriented, highly polished golden smartphone (iPhone style) displaying a social media profile interface. The background is a neutral, slightly gradient gray studio wall with subtle bokeh light flares. To the right of the subject, a large, reflective 3D metallic gold Instagram logo functions as a low pedestal, holding a white teacup and saucer. The interface on the golden phone is cream and gold colored. The phone's top status bar displays the time: [text1]. The profile title reads: [text2]. Statistics displayed are: [text3] [text4], [text5] [text6], [text7] [text8]. The main profile username is [text9], followed by the verification badge and the designation: [text10]. The profile bio includes the lines: [text11], [text12], [text13], and [text14]. A primary action button below the bio reads [text15]. Below the action button, two small circular avatar placeholders are labeled [