08,"name":"lq robot","tags":"psl, social","version":1,"premium":false,"template":"A high-quality, photorealistic sports-themed image featuring a central subject standing in a large, brightly lit cricket stadium. The subject is wearing a futuristic  athletic jersey with glowing cyan circuitry patterns printed on the chest. The subject is showing support for their favorite team. The color of the shirt are  based on the team selection. The logos on the shirt are based on team selection. The subject holds a cricket bat over their shoulder. The subject has cybernetic enhancements visible on their skin and arms, rendered in a realistic, metallic texture. The background shows a blurry, packed stadium crowd under stadium floodlights, with two large digital screens in the background displaying the text '[text1]' and '[text2]'. The jersey features logos including '[text3]', '[text4]', primary jersey branding '[text5]', '[text6]', and '[text7]', and a '[text9]' patch on the sleeve. Show a small watermark on the bottom right side with text: 'imagitor'. Use the attached photo as reference image, keep the facial features same as much as possible.\n","entities":"[{\"label\":\"Stadium screen text\",\"value\":\"LAHORE QALANDAR\",\"key\":\"[text1]\"},{\"label\":\"Secondary screen text\",\"value\":\"Pakistan Super League\",\"key\":\"[text2]\"},{\"label\":\"League logo text\",\"value\":\"PSL\",\"key\":\"[text3]\"},{\"label\":\"Team logo text\",\"value\":\"LAHORE QALANDAR\",\"key\":\"[text4]\"},{\"label\":\"Primary jersey branding\",\"value\":\"IMAGITOR\",\"key\":\"[text5]\"},{\"label\":\"Sub-branding text\",\"value\":\"AI Graphic Design App\",\"key\":\"[text6]\"},{\"label\":\"Sleeve brand\",\"value\":\"imagitor\",\"key\":\"[text7]\"},{\"label\":\"Sleeve band text\",\"value\":\"BooleanBites Ltd\",\"key\":\"[text8]\"},{\"label\":\"Captaincy indicator\",\"value\":\"C\",\"key\":\"[text9]\"}]","attachment":"dali\/img_1774504479767.png","thumb":"dali\/thumb_1774504479767.png","thumbSize":"32